INSERT INTO
                snapshot_recovery (
                    l1_batch_number,
                    l1_batch_timestamp,
                    l1_batch_root_hash,
                    miniblock_number,
                    miniblock_timestamp,
                    miniblock_hash,
                    protocol_version,
                    storage_logs_chunks_processed,
                    updated_at,
                    created_at
                )
            VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, NOW(), NOW())
